custom-meta.meta-value: The data underlying the results of this study are available upon request due to ethical and legal restrictions imposed by the QUT Research Ethics and Integrity Committee ( orei.enquiries@qut.edu.au) and the Public Health Act 2005. According to the Public Health Act 2005, data sharing of de-identified data sets with other persons are restricted. For data access requests, interested researchers can contact the Queensland Health is Executive Director, Communicable Diseases Branch, QLD (email: epi@health.qld.gov.au). Interested researchers must receive ethics approval before they can use the data.
